    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman is a true 'time capsule' vehicle, meticulously maintained to meet the highest standards. Finished in Agate Grey Metallic, the exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss with zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The interior is equally pristine, featuring black leather that still carries its original factory scent; the seat bolsters are firm with no signs of wear, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a documented single-owner history and a full binder of service records from authorized Porsche centers. It currently sits on a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires and has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality sports car that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
      "price": 44900.0,
