    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute gem, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always kept spotless and treated with so much love. If you're looking for a car that looks and feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Swing by and take a look, you're going to adore it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
