    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2005 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe. This specimen features the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission is paired with a variable M-differential lock for precise torque distribution. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full cooling system overhaul. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings and original dampers. Finished in Silver Grey Metallic with flawless paint depth readings and a clean DME report showing zero over-revs in ranges 1-5. An exceptional example for the discerning collector.",
